<div class="banner">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 id="main-title" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="3000" >RENT A SKILL</h1>
    <p >Start to figure out the superpowers available </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div>
    <h2 class="strong-underline" data-aos="zoom-in">OUR CONCEPT</h2>
    <p class="quote" >We believe people have skills. Great and <strong>unique</strong> skills. With us, you can use <strong>other people's abilities</strong>. Just like you'd rent a flat, you can now rent skills !</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="strong-underline" data-aos="flip-down">LATEST SKILLS</h2>

    <div class="row">
      <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
        <%= link_to skill_path(skill) do   %>
            <div class= col-sm>
              <div class="card-product" data-aos="zoom-in">
                <% if skill.photo.attachment %>
                  <%= cl_image_tag skill.photo.key, crop: :fill %>
                <% else  %>
                  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/skateboard.jpg" />
                <% end %>
                <div class="card-product-infos">
                  <h2 class="product-name"><%= skill.name %></h2>
                  <p><%= skill.description  %></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="strong-underline" data-aos="zoom-in">JUST GOOD STUFF</h2>
    <div class="image-asset">
      <img data-aos="fade-right" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dsaxkp6xo/image/upload/v1606305583/image_rent_1_p9grwe.png" alt="">
      <div class="asset" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="asset-list">
          <h5>Good for you</h5>
          <p>You will be able to enjoy the abilities of people all around the world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="asset-list">
          <h5>Have fun</h5>
          <p>Intellectual, physical, emotional, and everything you can imagine, you can have it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="asset-list">
          <h5>Show off</h5>
          <p>No matter why you rent a skill, it's always gonna be good for your showing it off. Impress a girl ? Easy ! Excell an exam ! Sure !</p>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
         <%= link_to "More Skills", skills_path, class: "button big" %>
        </div>
      </div>
     </div>


  <div>
    <h2 class="strong-underline" data-aos="zoom-in">REVIEWS</h2>
    <h3 class="title_reviews">What our customers think about our service</h3>
    <br>
  </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-around">
      <div data-aos="fade-right"  class="col-sm-5 card-review pt-3">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p><strong>Marie's opinion</strong>
          </div>
            On rent a skill, you can find a wide range of content with focus on skills for creative types. You will figure out every skill you want for one day or a week.</p>
        <div class="text-center">
         <%5.times do %>
          <i class="fas fa-star size"></i>
         <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-aos="fade-left" class="col-sm-5 card-review pt-3">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p><strong>Oscars's opinion</strong>
        </div>
        Rent a skill gives you instant access to thousands of new skills. It is easy to find high-quality skills that touch on topics surrounding themes of technology, business, creativity, and lifestyle.</p>
          <div class="text-center">
          <%5.times do %>
            <i class="fas fa-star size"></i>
          <% end %>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
